<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5301287>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. A–F, mandibular dentition, ventral view. G–L, right maxilliped 1 endopod and exopod, anterior view (epipod indicated by arrow). Eumunididae: A, G, Eumunida australis de Saint Laurent & Macpherson, 1990b (♂, pcl 12.9 mm, NMNZ Cr.21765); B, H, Pseudomunida fragilis Haig, 1979 (♀ ovig., pcl 20.5 mm, MNHN-Ga7507). Chirostylidae: C, I, Chirostylus dolichopus Ortmann, 1892 (♂, pcl 2.7 mm, MNHN station LA REUNION, MD32, CP172); D, J, Gastroptychus rogeri Baba, 2000 (♂, pcl 23.2 mm, NIWA 14555); E, K, Uroptychodes epigaster Baba, 2004 (♀, pcl 3.4 mm, NMNZ Cr.21766); F, L, Uroptychus cardus Ahyong & Poore, 2004 (♂, pcl 10.5 mm, NIWA 23086). Scale: A–F, not to scale; G, H, J, L = 1.00 mm; I, K = 0.45 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5301287/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

